                Mr. Dalton
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-93ac9571-87c6-411b-b4d0-5be75d02ed9f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
