                Sir S. Cripps
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0e64ee9c-d9f4-4c7f-b8b9-77b2cd6e0b2d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
