<p class="">Would the right hon. and learned Gentle man point out, purely for elucidation, what is the definition of "commodity" under paragraph (<em>d</em> )?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2224dfed-0d6e-4b82-b0d0-554553d946cb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
