            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e4fb2092-6cec-4d24-98a9-5b36284cf2a3">
                Mr. E. P. Smith  (Ashford)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e4fb2092-6cec-4d24-98a9-5b36284cf2a3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
