            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-6d62f793-bba7-455c-a2c6-8e76e96401cb">
                Mr. Deputy-Speaker (Mr. Hubert Beaumont)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6d62f793-bba7-455c-a2c6-8e76e96401cb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1945-12-12/debates/6c6b564f-6889-4f68-8e38-e5ea39409052/Anglo-AmericanFinancialAndEconomicDiscussions#contribution-6d62f793-bba7-455c-a2c6-8e76e96401cb">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The hon. Member is getting rather wide of the subject.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6d62f793-bba7-455c-a2c6-8e76e96401cb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1945-12-12/debates/6c6b564f-6889-4f68-8e38-e5ea39409052/Anglo-AmericanFinancialAndEconomicDiscussions#contribution-6d62f793-bba7-455c-a2c6-8e76e96401cb">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
