    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is the hon. Gentleman basing the good will and friendship of America on the question of this loan? Have we to buy it?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1e3e3272-1f5c-4b96-8c97-24af457c755b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
