<p class="">I did not suggest that. I said that it came from the wording of Article VII and is so stated in the document.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-80a3bd79-a03e-4def-81e2-78c436683c18" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
