            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-a1aa58e1-e261-4773-b462-b731046343d4">
                Sir William Darling  (Edinburgh, South)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a1aa58e1-e261-4773-b462-b731046343d4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
